Baby Oil Uses
Today we show you alternative uses of baby oil that hardly anyone knew.
these tricks are great and will surely be very helpful in your bathroom.
perfume your toilet, for this just apply a few drops inside the roll that supports the toilet paper.
then place the paper in its usual position and thatÂ´s it.
this will help you to have a very pleasant aroma in your bathroom.
I also want to show you the trick of putting toilet paper on a point.
fold in triangle.
when the toilet paper is like this, it means that your bathroom is freshly cleaned.
add a few drops of baby oil to a rag to give stainless steel a high shine.
add a few drops of baby oil cotton pads.
put the cotton pads in the bottom of the bin bag.
this is how the bathroom smells very good.
cleaning aluminium in the bathroom with baby oil not only gives it a shine, it also smells great.
